226
00:16:07,274 --> 00:16:09,974
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya tadinya mengira Anda hendak menebas leher musuh.</font>

227
00:16:10,914 --> 00:16:14,554
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah, iya, Anda bertanya pada saya bagaimana banding Yoon Seon Woo.</font>

228
00:16:14,654 --> 00:16:16,484
