314
00:21:00,834 --> 00:21:02,434
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun kemudian dia dibebaskan,</font>

315
00:21:03,204 --> 00:21:05,544
<font color=#FFFF00>sekalipun bukti-bukti sangat jelas.</font>

316
00:21:06,774 --> 00:21:08,174
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, Jaksa penanggung-jawabnya...</font>

317
00:21:08,814 --> 00:21:10,814
