00:21:26,064 --> 00:21:29,364
<font color=#FFFF00>Seakan ada perjanjian tidak kasat mata di sana.</font>

324
00:21:31,704 --> 00:21:33,264
<font color=#FFFF00>Kasus Yoon Seon Woo pun jelas,</font>

325
00:21:33,834 --> 00:21:36,134
