410
00:26:33,404 --> 00:26:35,204
<font color=#FFFF00>Aih, Kwon So Ra itu sungguh membuat saya gila.</font>

411
00:26:35,204 --> 00:26:38,444
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya semestinya mencengkeram dia.</font>

412
00:26:40,344 --> 00:26:43,614
